

fade/*/*/full:

- shown full screen
- if motif area fits in upper viewport half, no padding is needed
- if not, pad accordingly

fadeBg/*/*/full

- shown full screen
- motif area in upper viewport half will be overlayed by content of previous section
- if section is long enough: padding = motif area height

? what happens if there is not enough content
  fadeBg/scroll

scroll/*/*/*
scrollOver/*/*/*

- padding = motif area top + height

reveal/*/*/*

- padding = motif area top + height to allow showing whole picture

? what happens if there is not enough content
  reveal/scroll

